   ATTACK ON AMERICA
   The events of September 11, 2001 have shaken us all. Our hearts go out
   to everyone. We know that America is in a state of shock and we want to
   do all we can do to help. We are committed to providing services to the
   victims of these acts of terrorism in an expeditious and compassionate
   manner.
   In response to the tragedy that has struck our nation, we and other
   organizations are working together to ensure that information and
   services are readily available.
